# Epstein File Manager

A lightweight portable file manager for Windows.

Fast, clean and designed for efficient file management.

---

## Features

• Fast file browsing  
• Portable executable (no installation)  
• GitHub auto updater  
• Lightweight design  
• Clean UI  

More features coming soon.

---

## Download

Download the latest version here:

https://github.com/EinhornLab/Epstein-FileManager/releases

